		<title>狗狗最暖心的「5大」護主行為 都是愛的表現 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/06/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%9c%80%e6%9a%96%e5%bf%83%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c5%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e8%ad%b7%e4%b8%bb%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba-%e9%83%bd%e6%98%af%e6%84%9b%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be/</link>
		
